    <h1>Query Deserves Freshness (QDF)</h1>
    <p class="description">A Google ranking model that detects when a search query needs current information and temporarily prioritises newer content — letting new pages outrank established competitors. Understanding QDF turns publishing speed into a ranking advantage.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
