            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. QDF remains an active component of Google's ranking system. It has been joined by other freshness signals over the years, but the core model — detecting search volume spikes and prioritising recent content — still operates as originally described.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

